			<item>
				<title>美元在收紧，高波在释放(转载)</title>
				<link>https://entropydecrease.github.io/posts/%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83%E5%9C%A8%E6%94%B6%E7%B4%A7%E9%AB%98%E6%B3%A2%E5%9C%A8%E9%87%8A%E6%94%BE%E8%BD%AC%E8%BD%BD/</link>
				<pubDate>Fri, 17 Jul 2026 21:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
				<guid>https://entropydecrease.github.io/posts/%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83%E5%9C%A8%E6%94%B6%E7%B4%A7%E9%AB%98%E6%B3%A2%E5%9C%A8%E9%87%8A%E6%94%BE%E8%BD%AC%E8%BD%BD/</guid>
				<description>&lt;p&gt;转载自六里投资报的公众号文章： &lt;a&#xA;    href=&#34;https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/BWDnhjjYgKJV-5Uq4yTmvA&#34;target=&#34;_blank&#34;&#xA;    class=&#34;inline-flex items-center gap-1&#34;&#xA;  &gt;美元在收紧，高波在释放&lt;svg class=&#34;h-3 w-3 flex-shrink-0&#34; id=&#34;external-link&#34; xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 24 24&#34;&gt;&lt;path fill=&#34;none&#34; stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34; stroke-linecap=&#34;round&#34; stroke-linejoin=&#34;round&#34; stroke-width=&#34;2&#34; d=&#34;M15 3h6v6m-11 5L21 3m-3 10v6a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h6&#34;/&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;我的摘抄&#34;&gt;我的摘抄&lt;a href=&#34;#%e6%88%91%e7%9a%84%e6%91%98%e6%8a%84&#34; class=&#34;heading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;&#34;&gt;&lt;svg class=&#34;h-4 w-4&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 24 24&#34;&gt;&lt;g fill=&#34;none&#34; stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34; stroke-linecap=&#34;round&#34; stroke-linejoin=&#34;round&#34; stroke-width=&#34;2&#34;&gt;&lt;path d=&#34;M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71&#34;/&gt;&lt;path d=&#34;M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71&#34;/&gt;&lt;/g&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id=&#34;市场极致分化-资金全部涌向ai半导体&#34;&gt;市场极致分化 资金全部涌向AI半导体&lt;a href=&#34;#%e5%b8%82%e5%9c%ba%e6%9e%81%e8%87%b4%e5%88%86%e5%8c%96-%e8%b5%84%e9%87%91%e5%85%a8%e9%83%a8%e6%b6%8c%e5%90%91ai%e5%8d%8a%e5%af%bc%e4%bd%93&#34; class=&#34;heading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;&#34;&gt;&lt;svg class=&#34;h-4 w-4&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 24 24&#34;&gt;&lt;g fill=&#34;none&#34; stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34; stroke-linecap=&#34;round&#34; stroke-linejoin=&#34;round&#34; stroke-width=&#34;2&#34;&gt;&lt;path d=&#34;M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71&#34;/&gt;&lt;path d=&#34;M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71&#34;/&gt;&lt;/g&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;如果说到产业，全世界——至少从我们资本市场来讲——好像也只有一个产业，就是半导体。&lt;/p&gt;</description>
			</item>
			<item>
				<title>卡尔森对美伊协议的评价</title>
				<link>https://entropydecrease.github.io/posts/%E5%8D%A1%E5%B0%94%E6%A3%AE%E5%AF%B9%E7%BE%8E%E4%BC%8A%E5%8D%8F%E8%AE%AE%E7%9A%84%E8%AF%84%E4%BB%B7/</link>
				<pubDate>Wed, 24 Jun 2026 19:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
				<guid>https://entropydecrease.github.io/posts/%E5%8D%A1%E5%B0%94%E6%A3%AE%E5%AF%B9%E7%BE%8E%E4%BC%8A%E5%8D%8F%E8%AE%AE%E7%9A%84%E8%AF%84%E4%BB%B7/</guid>
				<description>&lt;p&gt;In your mindset, you may image that, the American empire ending someday, probably in like a conflagration in some sort of conflict with another great power. If you had to pick one, you would imagine the end might come in a dispute over Taiwan &amp;ndash; formally &amp;lsquo;Formosa&amp;rsquo;, the island off mainland China that China considers part of its country. And the United States has sort of informally suggested that it would defend the Taiwan&amp;rsquo;s sovereignty. And periodically that part of the world, South China Sea, pops into the news, and you think, wow, that that could be a big deal if, you know, we actually had a war with China, because every year they get stronger, they have a bigger economy than ours, and you can kind of imagine some reckless American leader destroying American power over taiwan. But you probably never imagine that the end of American empire would come in a little over a hundred day conflict, with a little rogue state on the Persian gulf that has the 34th largest economy in the world, a country called Iran.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
			</item>
			<item>
				<title>委内瑞拉事件后续的思考</title>
				<link>https://entropydecrease.github.io/posts/venezuela2/</link>
				<pubDate>Sat, 10 Jan 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
				<guid>https://entropydecrease.github.io/posts/venezuela2/</guid>
				<description>&lt;p&gt;委内瑞拉总统被掳走的后续事件：&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;美国懂王一派解释关于入侵委内瑞拉的理由，主要是石油，委的石油应该为美国所拥有，而不能为中俄所买。&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;美国国内有反对声音，因为此举不合法。但是懂王一派完全不理会，以&lt;a&#xA;    href=&#34;https://news.ifeng.com/c/8pkp9WmGl91&#34;target=&#34;_blank&#34;&#xA;    class=&#34;inline-flex items-center gap-1&#34;&#xA;  &gt;白宫副幕僚长&lt;svg class=&#34;h-3 w-3 flex-shrink-0&#34; id=&#34;external-link&#34; xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 24 24&#34;&gt;&lt;path fill=&#34;none&#34; stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34; stroke-linecap=&#34;round&#34; stroke-linejoin=&#34;round&#34; stroke-width=&#34;2&#34; d=&#34;M15 3h6v6m-11 5L21 3m-3 10v6a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h6&#34;/&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;的言论最为坦诚、富有哲理：“&lt;strong&gt;我们生活在这样一个世界里，你可以畅谈国际礼仪什么的，请便。但我们生活在一个真实的世界里，一个由实力、武力和权力统治的世界。这就是世界的铁律，自古以来就是如此。&lt;/strong&gt;”&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;一些盟友不作声，也有一些欧洲国家反对，例如西班牙。南美国家也有反对。中俄当然抨击。&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;懂王开始谈论要得到格陵兰岛，理由也很简单，美国需要。丹麦反对，格陵兰所有政党联名反对。&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;懂王召集国内石油公司讨论在委内瑞拉投资开采石油，似乎未得响应。理由也简单，投资石油领域周期太长，还没建设好，懂王任期就结束了，委内瑞拉政局未定，变数太大。&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&#xA;&lt;figure&#xA;  class=&#34;image-figure not-prose my-8&#34;&#xA;  data-lightbox-enabled=&#34;&#xA;    false&#xA;  &#34;&#xA;  data-gallery-type=&#34;auto&#34;&#xA;  data-image-width=&#34;1322&#34;&#xA;  data-image-height=&#34;1310&#34;&#xA;  data-image-src=&#34;https://entropydecrease.github.io/posts/venezuela2/resources/1.png&#34;&#xA;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;image-container&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;img&#xA;    src=&#34;https://entropydecrease.github.io/posts/venezuela2/resources/1.png&#34;&#xA;    alt=&#34;&#34;&#xA;    &#xA;    &#xA;      &#xA;      &#xA;        &#xA;          width=&#34;1322&#34; height=&#34;1310&#34;&#xA;        &#xA;      &#xA;    &#xA;    loading=&#34;lazy&#34;&#xA;    decoding=&#34;async&#34;&#xA;    data-gallery-src=&#34;https://entropydecrease.github.io/posts/venezuela2/resources/1.png&#34;&#xA;    data-gallery-alt=&#34;&#34;&#xA;    data-gallery-title=&#34;&#34;&#xA;  /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&#xA;  &lt;/figure&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;figure&#xA;  class=&#34;image-figure not-prose my-8&#34;&#xA;  data-lightbox-enabled=&#34;&#xA;    false&#xA;  &#34;&#xA;  data-gallery-type=&#34;auto&#34;&#xA;  data-image-width=&#34;1322&#34;&#xA;  data-image-height=&#34;792&#34;&#xA;  data-image-src=&#34;https://entropydecrease.github.io/posts/venezuela2/resources/2.png&#34;&#xA;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;image-container&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;img&#xA;    src=&#34;https://entropydecrease.github.io/posts/venezuela2/resources/2.png&#34;&#xA;    alt=&#34;&#34;&#xA;    &#xA;    &#xA;      &#xA;      &#xA;        &#xA;          width=&#34;1322&#34; height=&#34;792&#34;&#xA;        &#xA;      &#xA;    &#xA;    loading=&#34;lazy&#34;&#xA;    decoding=&#34;async&#34;&#xA;    data-gallery-src=&#34;https://entropydecrease.github.io/posts/venezuela2/resources/2.png&#34;&#xA;    data-gallery-alt=&#34;&#34;&#xA;    data-gallery-title=&#34;&#34;&#xA;  /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&#xA;  &lt;/figure&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;figure&#xA;  class=&#34;image-figure not-prose my-8&#34;&#xA;  data-lightbox-enabled=&#34;&#xA;    false&#xA;  &#34;&#xA;  data-gallery-type=&#34;auto&#34;&#xA;  data-image-width=&#34;1322&#34;&#xA;  data-image-height=&#34;792&#34;&#xA;  data-image-src=&#34;https://entropydecrease.github.io/posts/venezuela2/resources/3.png&#34;&#xA;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;image-container&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;img&#xA;    src=&#34;https://entropydecrease.github.io/posts/venezuela2/resources/3.png&#34;&#xA;    alt=&#34;&#34;&#xA;    &#xA;    &#xA;      &#xA;      &#xA;        &#xA;          width=&#34;1322&#34; height=&#34;792&#34;&#xA;        &#xA;      &#xA;    &#xA;    loading=&#34;lazy&#34;&#xA;    decoding=&#34;async&#34;&#xA;    data-gallery-src=&#34;https://entropydecrease.github.io/posts/venezuela2/resources/3.png&#34;&#xA;    data-gallery-alt=&#34;&#34;&#xA;    data-gallery-title=&#34;&#34;&#xA;  /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&#xA;  &lt;/figure&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;figure&#xA;  class=&#34;image-figure not-prose my-8&#34;&#xA;  data-lightbox-enabled=&#34;&#xA;    false&#xA;  &#34;&#xA;  data-gallery-type=&#34;auto&#34;&#xA;  data-image-width=&#34;1540&#34;&#xA;  data-image-height=&#34;1778&#34;&#xA;  data-image-src=&#34;https://entropydecrease.github.io/posts/venezuela2/resources/5.png&#34;&#xA;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;image-container&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;img&#xA;    src=&#34;https://entropydecrease.github.io/posts/venezuela2/resources/5.png&#34;&#xA;    alt=&#34;&#34;&#xA;    &#xA;    &#xA;      &#xA;      &#xA;        &#xA;          width=&#34;1540&#34; height=&#34;1778&#34;&#xA;        &#xA;      &#xA;    &#xA;    loading=&#34;lazy&#34;&#xA;    decoding=&#34;async&#34;&#xA;    data-gallery-src=&#34;https://entropydecrease.github.io/posts/venezuela2/resources/5.png&#34;&#xA;    data-gallery-alt=&#34;&#34;&#xA;    data-gallery-title=&#34;&#34;&#xA;  /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&#xA;  &lt;/figure&gt;&#xA;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
			</item>
			<item>
				<title>委内瑞拉</title>
				<link>https://entropydecrease.github.io/posts/venezuela/</link>
				<pubDate>Sat, 03 Jan 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
				<guid>https://entropydecrease.github.io/posts/venezuela/</guid>
				<description>&lt;p&gt;晚上和朋友吃饭的时候，看了一下手机，委内瑞拉总统被美国捉走了。又是一个改变国际政治局势的大势，可以与俄罗斯进攻乌克兰、以色列侵略加沙、美国袭击伊朗并列，并且是影响美洲格局的一个重大事件。&lt;/p&gt;</description>
			</item>
